**src/ layout:** Prevents accidental local imports, forces proper editable install, catches import errors.

**One assert per test:** Pinpoints failure, single purpose, easier skip/xfail.

**Fixtures over setUp/tearDown:** Composable, explicit, scoped, modular via conftest.py.

**TDD:** Red (failing test defines contract) → Green (minimal pass) → Refactor (tests guard correctness).
